<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bir kere b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m niye iyiydi? Eski karakterleri g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k. Yeni seriyle hayat</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">za giren ama yine uzun s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">redir g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rmedi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">imiz karakterler de vard</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Sonra en </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nemlisi </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ndash;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">bence- Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un gitar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yla sahneye </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ışı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">! 8. sezonda </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">o</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">u izleyici Clara</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n hal ve hareketlerinden s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400