<p><!-- pagebreak --></p>
<p><img src="/uploads/editor/foto1s.jpg" alt="Milyonların katili olacak bir &ccedil;ocuk g&ouml;r&uuml;yorsunuz." width="640" height="356" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Neyse, b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">me gelecek olursak. Bir sava</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">şı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n ortas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">na d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yoruz. Ben Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">u g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ğ&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z ana kadar hep Matt Smith</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">li zamanlar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">and</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ığı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yorum b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n. Atmosfer tam da ona g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">reydi. Bu arada Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">u g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rmekten kast</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m gitar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yla sahneye </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">kt</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ığı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">me kadar olan yerlerdi. Yoksa sava</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">şı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n ortas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nda ufakl</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ığ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">a yard</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m etti</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ini biliyorum. Biri ufakl</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">dedi?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cidden </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">a</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">şı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rt</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">c</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">, </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rk</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">c</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ve heyecan dolu de</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">il miydi? Kesinlikle </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yleydi! Doctor </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ocu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">a ad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">sordu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">unda ald</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ığı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z yan</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t, b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n geri kalan</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yla ilgili az da olsa bize bilgi vermi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">oldu! Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un en b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">manlar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ndan birisi olan Davros ufac</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k, </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rkek haliyle kar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">şı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">zda duruyordu. Etraf</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı &ldquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">el may</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nlar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı&rdquo; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">denilen yarat</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">klarla sar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Daha </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nce g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rmedi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">imiz yarat</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">klar ya da ad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">na her ne derseniz. Sizi kapt</span><span style="font-w