<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">H</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">mm! Kim olacakt</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ki ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ka? Veeee Missy ortaya </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yor. Eski Master yeni Missy desek daha do</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ru. A</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">as</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">8. sezonda b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n gizem onun </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">zerindeydi ancak onun hakk</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ndaki teoriler belliydi ve hepsi de do</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ru </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">kt</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Zaten </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lmedi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ini de biliyorduk. Missy (Master) </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yle kolay kurtulabilece</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">iniz bir karakter de</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><