<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">İş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">te burada Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un muhte</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">em giri</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ini g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yoruz. Bilenler vard</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r zaten Peter Capaldi bu b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">mde gitar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">kendisi </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">al</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yor. Zaten gitar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">tutu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">undan, el hareketlerine her </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ey bunu belli ediyor ama bilmeyenler i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">in s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yleyeyim dedim. Hele de Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un Missy ve Clara</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rd</span><span style="font-weight: 40