<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Biliyoruz ki yeni Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un yani 12</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nin sar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lma huyu pek yok. Ancak Clara</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nce beklentileri a</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">an bir sar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lmas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">var. Doctor </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lece</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ini biliyor. Ya da buna benzer bir </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ey. Sonu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ta </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lmeyecek ama i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">in i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">inde garip </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eyler var. B</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">papyon takarak ge</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">irmi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Ondan </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nce de uzun bir atk</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yla dola</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ış </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">mesela. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bu benim partim ve b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n benler davetli</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rdquo; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">diyor. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Clara ve Missy</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nin sahneye </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">kmas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ndan biraz sonra Koloni Sarff belirir. Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un onunla gelmesini, Davros</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lmeden </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nce onunla konu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">acak </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eyleri oldu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">unu s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yler. Doctor bunu kimseye zarar vermeyece</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">i ko</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">uluyla kabul eder. Eh! O kadar yol gelmi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">olan Clara ve Missy</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nin de orada kalacak halleri yoktu ya. </span></p>
