<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Doctor ve Davros nihayet bulu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">uyorlar. Ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">alar ve o eski h</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rsl</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">konu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">malar yok. Sanki Davros yorgun d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">gibi. Davros neden geldi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ini biliyor musun? diyor. Doctor </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Anlad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rdquo; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">diyor. Bir anda g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nt</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ye 4. Doctor olarak bildi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">imiz Tom Baker</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">u </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yor. Evet, Moffat</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;ı </span><span style="font-