<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bu s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rada Clara ve Missy tutsak olduklar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">h</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">creden kurtulurlar ve d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ış</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ya </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">karlar. Asl</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nda uzayda bir kaps</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">erisinde oldu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">unu sand</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ığı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z yer Skaro</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nun kendisidir. Yani Daleklerin Gezegeni, Missy</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nin deyimiyle, her </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eyin ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lang</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">c</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı&hellip;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Zaten b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n sonuna geldik. Missy ve Clara tekrar yakalan</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rlar. Yine bizi heyecanland</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">racak karakterler g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z. Zaten fragmanlardan biliyorduk. Y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ce Dalekler diye </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">evirebilece</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">im, klasik seri Daleklerini g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yoruz. Tardis ele ge</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">irilmi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">tir ve yok edilecektir. Davros</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un bu konuda yapaca</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">hi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">bir </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eyi yoktur. Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un da eli kolu ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r. S</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rayla Missy ve Clara, Daleklerin kurban</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">olurlar. Elbette ikisinin </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">de bu kadar kolay olmayacak. Ancak Clara </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ld</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ğ&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nde Doctor</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">un y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ndeki ac</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">verici ifadeyi g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rmeyen yoktur herhalde. </span></p>
